dc_description_s: The PA_Portable_X_Ray_2016 layer contains the latitude and longitude coordinates of 15 portable X-ray centers in Pennsylvania. When possible, efforts were made to confirm the rooftop location of each portable X-ray center. The accuracy of geocoding is available in Geocoding Certainty attribute field (Geocoding Certainty: Rooftop="00", Street="01", Zip Centroid="04", Not geocoded="99"). Latitude and longitude fields are recorded in the WGS 1984 coordinate system.Last updated: 11/09/2016Contact Us: Pennsylvania Department of HealthDivision of Health InformaticsRA-DHICONTACTUS@pa.gov717-782-2448
